## ЁЯОп ржкрзНрж░рждрж┐ржЯрж┐ ржоржбрж┐ржЙрж▓рзЗрж░ Key Features:

### User Module (рж╕ржкрзНрждрж╛рж╣ рзи):
- тЬЕ Login with username/password/branch
- тЬЕ Role-based access control
- тЬЕ Session management (30 minutes timeout)
- тЬЕ Failed login attempt tracking (3 attempts тЖТ lock 5 minutes)
- тЬЕ Password change functionality
- тЬЕ User activity logging

### Customer Module (рж╕ржкрзНрждрж╛рж╣ рзй):
- тЬЕ Create customer with NID verification
- тЬЕ Generate 5-digit account number
- тЬЕ Account types: Savings (111) / Current (222)
- тЬЕ Maker approval workflow
- тЬЕ Customer search by NID/Account Number

### Transaction Module (рж╕ржкрзНрждрж╛рж╣ рзк):
- тЬЕ Deposit validation (active account, amount > 0, limits)
- тЬЕ Withdrawal validation (sufficient balance, cash drawer check)
- тЬЕ Batch number generation
- тЬЕ Maker approval required
- тЬЕ Cash drawer balance update

### GL Module (рж╕ржкрзНрждрж╛рж╣ рзл):
- тЬЕ Double-entry (Debit/Credit)
- тЬЕ GL-1001: Cash (Asset)
- тЬЕ GL-2001: Customer Deposits (Liability)
- тЬЕ Atomic transaction (COMMIT/ROLLBACK)
- тЬЕ Pre-GL check (approved but not posted)

### Reconciliation Module (рж╕ржкрзНрждрж╛рж╣ рзм):
- тЬЕ GL-2001 vs Customer Sub-ledger
- тЬЕ GL-1001 vs Cash Drawer Sub-ledger
- тЬЕ Trial Balance check (╬гDebit = ╬гCredit)
- тЬЕ Cash proof (physical vs system)
- тЬЕ Mismatch detection and resolution

